unction is advisable.', 'Synergism', 'The use of naltrexone with other potentially hepatotoxic agents should be avoided whenever possible (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/23569/', '', 'Acetylsalicylic acid, Naloxone, Naltrexone, Rabeprazole, Misoprostol, Chondroitin sulfate, Glucosamine, Esomeprazole, Tamsulosin, Tinidazole, Ascorbic acid, More', 'Tapentadol, Oxymorphone, Dezocine, Opium, Celecoxib, Naloxone, Nalbuphine, Diamorphine, Acamprosate, Lofexidine, Levacetylmethadol, More', 1767369485);
